<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lo">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="ແຜງຄວບຄຸມຜູ້ດູແລລະບົບຊື້-ຂາຍລົດມືສອງ">
    <title>ແຜງຄວບຄຸມແອດມິນ</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Lao:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/admin/dashboard">
                <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo" style="height: 80px; margin-right: 15px;">
                ແຜງຄວບຄຸມແອດມິນ
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/manage-car">ຈັດການລົດ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/add-car">ເພີ່ມລົດໃໝ່</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/manage-sell-requests">ຈັດການຄຳຂໍຂາຍ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/">ໜ້າຫຼັກ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link text-danger" href="/admin/logout" onclick="return confirm('ທ່ານແນ່ໃຈບໍ່ທີ່ຈະອອກຈາກລະບົບ?');">ອອກຈາກລະບົບ</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <div class="card bg-dark text-light">
            <div class="card-header bg-gold text-dark">
                <h2>ແຜງຄວບຄຸມຜູ້ດູແລລະບົບ</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3>ພາບລວມຂອງລະບົບ</h3>
                <div class="row mt-4">
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                        <div class="card bg-dark text-light border border-gold">
                            <div class="card-body text-center">
                                <h4>ຈຳນວນລົດທັງໝົດ</h4>
                                <p class="display-6"><%- totalCars || 0 %></p>
                                <a href="/admin/manage-car" class="btn btn-gold btn-sm">ເບິ່ງລົດທັງໝົດ</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                        <div class="card bg-dark text-light border border-gold">
                            <div class="card-body text-center">
                                <h4>ຄຳຂໍຂາຍທີ່ລໍຖ້າ</h4>
                                <p class="display-6"><%- pendingRequests || 0 %></p>
                                <a href="/admin/manage-sell-requests" class="btn btn-gold btn-sm">ຈັດການຄຳຂໍ</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                        <div class="card bg-dark text-light border border-gold">
                            <div class="card-body text-center">
                                <h4>ລົດພຣີມຽມ</h4>
                                <p class="display-6"><%- premiumCars || 0 %></p>
                                <a href="/admin/manage-car" class="btn btn-gold btn-sm">ເບິ່ງລົດພຣີມຽມ</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h3 class="mt-5">ການດຳເນີນການດ່ວນ</h3>
                <div class="row mt-3">
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                        <a href="/admin/manage-car" class="btn btn-gold w-100">ຈັດການລົດທັງໝົດ</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                        <a href="/admin/add-car" class="btn btn-gold w-100">ເພີ່ມລົດໃໝ່</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                        <a href="/admin/manage-sell-requests" class="btn btn-gold w-100">ຈັດການຄຳຂໍຂາຍ</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h3 class="mt-5">ສະຖິຕິລົດຕາມປະເພດ</h3>
                <div class="row mt-3">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="card bg-dark text-light border border-gold">
                            <div class="card-body text-center">
                                <h5>ລົດເກົງ (Sedan)</h5>
                                <p><%- sedanCount || 0 %> ຄັນ</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="card bg-dark text-light border border-gold">
                            <div class="card-body text-center">
                                <h5>ລົດແຮທຊ໌ແບັກ (Hatchback)</h5>
                                <p><%- hatchbackCount || 0 %> ຄັນ</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="card bg-dark text-light border border-gold">
                            <div class="card-body text-center">
                                <h5>ລົດກະບະ (Pickup)</h5>
                                <p><%- pickupCount || 0 %> ຄັນ</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="card bg-dark text-light border border-gold">
                            <div class="card-body text-center">
                                <h5>ລົດຄຣອສໂອເວີ (Crossover)</h5>
                                <p><%- crossoverCount || 0 %> ຄັນ</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="card bg-dark text-light border border-gold">
                            <div class="card-body text-center">
                                <h5>ລົດ SUV</h5>
                                <p><%- suvCount || 0 %> ຄັນ</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="card bg-dark text-light border border-gold">
                            <div class="card-body text-center">
                                <h5>ລົດ PPV</h5>
                                <p><%- ppvCount || 0 %> ຄັນ</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="card bg-dark text-light border border-gold">
                            <div class="card-body text-center">
                                <h5>ລົດ MPV</h5>
                                <p><%- mpvCount || 0 %> ຄັນ</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- โฆษณา -->
                <div class="ad-section mt-4">
                    <h3>ປະກັນພັຍລົດຍົນ</h3>
                    <p>ສົນໃຈປະກັນພັຍລົດທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດສຳລັບທ່ານ? ຕິດຕໍ່ພວກເຮົາສຳລັບຂໍ້ສະເໜີພິເສດ!</p>
                    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">ສອບຖາມເພີ່ມເຕີມ</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer text-center bg-dark text-gold">
        <div class="container">
            <p>ທີ່ຢູ່: ນະຄອນຫຼວງວຽງຈັນ, ປະເທດລາວ</p>
            <p>ໂທ: +856 20 1234 5678</p>
            <p>ອີເມວ: contact@yourcarwebsite.com</p>
            <p>ຕິດຕາມພວກເຮົາ:
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/yourpage" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">Facebook</a> |
                <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@your.tiktok" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">TikTok</a>
            </p>
            <p>ດາວໂຫຼດແອັບ:
                <a href="https://play.google.com/store" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">Google Play</a> |
                <a href="https://www.apple.com/app-store/" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">App Store</a>
            </p>
            <p>© 2025 Used Car Sales. ສະຫງວນລິຂະສິດ.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>